Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.01,0:00:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾經很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很想大哭一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.21,0:00:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.58,0:00:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不論何時也不是孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.29,0:00:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遙遠的夢想在閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.03,0:00:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將它找回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.60,0:00:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把雙眼閉上便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.57,0:00:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在心中的一個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.67,0:00:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算留下傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.78,0:00:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要害怕 現在是兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.49,0:01:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要放棄 Step by step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.69,0:01:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓著夢想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.39,0:01:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,經常也和你一起向明天邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.70,0:01:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,繼續前進 Step by step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.44,0:01:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想堅信著 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.61,0:01:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想向著天空大聲呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.15,0:01:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,燃燒著 in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.51,0:02:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老公公,創界山的彩虹何時看也這麼美麗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對,這也是全靠救世主渡的關係\N真是感激呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很感謝呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.96,0:02:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.83,0:02:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,推啊!推啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:03:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子勝!火美子第一!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.80,0:03:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彩虹變得看不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.20,0:03:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創界山的彩虹在消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.85,0:03:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,母后南鬥七星變成那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.23,0:03:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我感覺到星界山,發出邪惡之氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.97,0:03:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個世界再次有危險迫近了,要叫救世主渡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主渡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.57,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 渡 渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救護車!救護車!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.49,0:03:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一話\N歸來了的(救護車)救世主!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接得好!渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵!渡快點擲出來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.68,0:04:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞬 你這麼想看…我的珍貴技術嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.13,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的是玩什麼也這麼能手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.43,0:04:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡!怎能只有渡一個威風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.03,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了,由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞬,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.65,0:04:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由美,不是這樣擲的\N你看看我吧,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡那混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對,就這樣一口氣擲出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.20,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡真水皮,你自己去拾回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.91,0:05:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.52,0:05:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由美,我會去拾的了\N你和瞬一起在那邊等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要小心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.12,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由美 快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.21,0:05:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?為什麼龍神丸會在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我啊,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是龍…龍神丸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.99,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯 真的是龍神丸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,但是為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.94,0:06:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,創界山又再有危機迫近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?但是多惡達不是已經被打敗了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.12,0:06:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有新的魔界之徒出現了,他的名字是多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.10,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多壞達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.30,0:06:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創界山再次需要救世主渡的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能跟我一起去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在?\N沒錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以和媽媽說一聲嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要盡快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.54,0:06:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我叫了瞬和由美等我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起,由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧!龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊!是救世主渡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救護車!救護車!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子 你好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好!來得好啊,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們已在這裏等了你十天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.57,0:08:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,十天?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.47,0:08:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,不用再打招呼了\N快點趕去聖龍殿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聖龍殿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起立,敬禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,請你看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有七顆星排在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.40,0:08:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然我們看到的是七顆星,但那裏其實是星界山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星界山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.64,0:08:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星界山和這個世界是有很多親密關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.84,0:08:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傳說那七顆星的光耀是創界山彩虹力量的來源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.00,0:08:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個星界山現在好像被一個叫多壞達的魔界使者支配了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.72,0:08:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多壞達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是多惡達的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.43,0:08:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星界山的星失去了光耀\N創界山彩虹的顏色也會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個世界會永遠活在黑暗之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很喜歡吃蕎頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.67,0:09:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此,你要以救世主的身份和龍神丸一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.68,0:09:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到星界山的第七星界把多壞達消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.95,0:09:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃?可是…多壞達很強的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很強,很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個多惡達也已打得那麼辛苦了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.26,0:09:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!創界山的彩虹消失了會變成怎樣你也會知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.67,0:09:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多壞達一定會連創界山也一起支配的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!\N奮鬥!奮鬥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.28,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是星界山是在天空上吧\N龍神丸又不能飛的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.42,0:09:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個不用擔心\N我們會把龍神丸發射上天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發射?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.79,0:10:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爆發!爆發!爆發!\N爆發?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.40,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真有型!要發射上太空嗎?\N我去,我要去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.81,0:10:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘩!比之前的更有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這對鞋有滾軸鞋的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.24,0:10:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,這把是星龍劍是能夠蔻星宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.94,0:10:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藏有宇宙力量的劍 你拿它去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.75,0:11:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星龍劍嗎?\N星界山也許有很多艱難的事在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們準備了一些不時之需
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是飯團啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.80,0:11:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這些不是飯團 而是神奇飯團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有很神奇力量的飯團呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那用法呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在危急的時候吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃了會怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.94,0:11:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個呢!到時候再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神奇飯團嗎?真有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.01,0:11:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,把火美子頭上的東西借給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?變成三角形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎會這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是回轉龍圓盤,那應該也能成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.47,0:11:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保護你的重要道具吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.31,0:11:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回轉龍圓盤嗎?有這麼多道具便沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.65,0:12:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之後等武一郎師傅和古拿瑪來到便完美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.82,0:12:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?師傅和古拿瑪有什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已發射了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.46,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武一郎和古拿瑪三日前已向星界山進發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那師傅跟古拿瑪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.44,0:12:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想他們已經平安的到達星界山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.94,0:12:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅…古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去星界山吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.16,0:12:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸在外面等著你\N渡,請你也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.30,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我之後也一定會去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎…虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,渡,趕快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唷!渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難…難道是用這個去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恩,就用那個去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.24,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不要說笑了,那東西怎可能飛上宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.31,0:13:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有火箭或穿梭機之類嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.58,0:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什麼東西?不明白嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,快點來吧! 點火 萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.09,0:13:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 快點乘上龍神丸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.06,0:14:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還不快點!\N等…等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒數 10、 9、 8…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.17,0:14:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位快抬渡去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等…等等 停手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.94,0:14:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,100、2、7、4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.11,0:14:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好了 要快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行了 趕不及了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,6、9、5…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.30,0:14:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要這樣 會在宇宙沒空氣死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,7、3、爆炸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.85,0:14:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要好好加油啊,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.52,0:14:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子在哪裏啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.04,0:15:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子\N咦?有空氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.11,0:15:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 下面的數字是這部魔神海盜船的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊的是攻擊力 是力量的強度呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.56,0:15:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊的是頭腦 數字越高表示魔神的頭腦越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.96,0:15:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後最後的是速度 表示移動的速度有多快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.64,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是牛奶最好喝\N這樣不單是24小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,100小時也能作戰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.89,0:16:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有野鴨飛近\N不,是有魔神來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.93,0:16:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣呢?去會會他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.00,0:16:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!有魔神出現了,不要大意!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.47,0:16:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說不要大意,但這樣子可以做什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.71,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先來一發見面禮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家夥幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是看守星界山入口的天空的海盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.79,0:16:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海盜王雙霸王大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.36,0:16:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海盜?海盜不是在海裏的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.60,0:16:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會答你這麼瑣碎的問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.28,0:17:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我除了蕎頭外,第二喜歡的便是牛奶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.40,0:17:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫火美子,是忍部一族第十三代的首領啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.00,0:17:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首領?那我們也是一樣了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.66,0:17:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一樣了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.47,0:17:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個怎樣也好,小鬼給我消失!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,火美子!\N龍神丸,想想辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.24,0:17:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只能直線向前飛,什麼也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.26,0:17:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好,是我重要的獵物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,用劍把網切開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會讓你得手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀!渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.42,0:18:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用這個收拾你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.19,0:18:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是戰神丸的矛\N那麼說師傅是被這家夥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我不會輸的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.37,0:18:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是…救世主…渡啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那些光是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,你的外形變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.80,0:19:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡的勇氣令星界山的星宿賜予了我力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來!渡,和我一起戰鬥吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛吧,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.67,0:19:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厲害,有了翼\N力量增強了,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.28,0:19:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯!\N好,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.52,0:19:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟打我,這樣便讓你嘗嘗這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.39,0:20:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騎單車(bai kin gu)除去了gu是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.70,0:20:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騎單車不要了gu是…海盜(bai kin)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,答對了!獎品便是中了會肚痛的海盜飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.34,0:20:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家夥在打中目標之前會一直追下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.29,0:20:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再送多你一發,這次是中了會牙痛的海盜飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.56,0:20:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行,這樣下去會被追上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.20,0:20:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!龍神丸,向上飛吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向上飛?我有個好辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,交給你吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,逃也沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.25,0:21:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,急降下吧!好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.56,0:21:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到差不多撞到為止才避開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.43,0:21:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.41,0:21:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.67,0:21:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子很痛啊,牙好痛啊!\N肚子很痛,牙很痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是機會了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.38,0:21:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.78,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.17,0:21:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能24小時作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.01,0:21:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,第一!\N渡,偉大!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.85,0:22:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,終於到星界山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.04,0:22:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?這個胸口 在驅跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.50,0:22:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.13,0:22:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop!已不能停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.42,0:22:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連你也一個勁兒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.82,0:22:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,油門不用放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.23,0:22:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直踏著 Go!Go!Go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.40,0:22:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.60,0:23:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為是速度的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.84,0:23:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,TONIGHT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.01,0:23:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.75,0:23:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能夠抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.28,0:23:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直望著的瞳孔湧上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.25,0:23:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.59,0:23:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今夜 MY LOVE
